This paper is primarily focused on digital forensics, which falls under the category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves the use of static analysis techniques, which could be categorized under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.SE (Software Engineering). Additionally, the paper involves the identification of files and data, which could be categorized under cs.DB (Databases) and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
